155
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:57,940
Em-yrram.

156
00:17:58,040 --> 00:18:00,740
- No, I'm not playing this game.
- Say it, it's serious.

157
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,840
It's very serious.

158
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,800
Yrram.

159
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,120
Marry me.

160
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:13,860
No... I'm not gonna marry you.
